the world is full of empty promises.
those always hurt the most.
who knows what will happen.
I sure don't.
but I know what I want to happen.
maybe it will.
most likely it won't.

I know none of this makes sense to anyone.
sadly, it makes perfect sense to me.
maybe someday the world will see.
doubt it.

so yeah... I'm REALLY bored, that's pretty much the only reason I'm on here.. yeah, bad I know... but anyways, I haven't been doing much, just working and packing... I saw an alpaca the other day.. yeah.. and now I'm all depressed cuz I got my first going away present today, it was from my church.. they gave me a picture of the stained glass window, a stuffed bear (I named it Elmer), and a moose bracelet.. yeah... I cried earlier... I'm really getting sad about this move... 10 more days... then I have to grow up.. oh, I got a car! its already in Indiana, its pretty, I named it Skiba... yeah... and yeah... I dunno.. lately I've been having dreams of El Paso.. its weird.. I think its my subconsious telling me I'm really sad about moving, and I think moving from el paso was the worse move emotionally, and this move is reserecting those old feelings of sadness.. yeah... wow, that was deep.. yeah.. but I think I"m going to go.. its like 3 in the morning, and I have to pee.. so I'm off like a prom dress...

aww man, I totally missed going good on posts every day, but there isn't much to post about... what can you say about alaska? After you do everything, there's absoultely nothing left to do.. yeah, that made a whole lot of sence.. but yeah.. anyways... I have a different journal, which I update a heck of a lot more often... I don't know if any of you have an xanga... but my journal is www.xanga.com/killmewithaspork .. yeah... you guys should check it out, I think its better then my livejournal... so yeah... I think I'm going to go now.... I'm off like a prom dress...

oky, this is gettin crazy... so many updates in a ROW! lol.. yeah.. but anyways, went to the mall today.. woot... we got walkie-talkies and were messing with people on them.. good times, good times... the bathroom there had a flickery light, so it was like peeing in a rave... lol.. yeah, then tried to hang with Raul, but he was busy, and his co-worker-lady looked like she was going to eat us, so we left.. and we got smoothies.. and I got a button that says "drop it like its hot" and a checkered tie, and another button that says "too cool for school", just cuz I am.. NOW... lol... and I also got my Kaiser Chiefs cd! WOOT! Instant gratification.... good times, good times... I danced in the rain today, now I'm all wet, and I ran threw the sprinkler, just cuz I CAN... lol...  then yeah, I dunno... I want to make a movie, but I don't know what it should be about... any suggestions? it can be a movie-movie or a music video-movie or a documentry-movie, I'm not picky.. lol.. but I think I'm off like a prom dress...

Oh my gosh! I'm actually on... AND updating!! Whoa! So yes... I'm graduated! Woot! yeah... lets see.. what else... umm.. umm... I'm moving in a few months.. to Indiana! woot.. go me! what else? I've been really bored lately, but yeah, school was fun, almost sad its over... ALMOST.. haha... what else? umm... umm... I've been making movies A LOT lately! Very fun! umm.. I don't know what else really... its been so long.. and SO much has happened that I can't even think of where to even start.. which makes it difficult... I'm going to try to update more often... hopefully, now cuz I got a laptop for graduation.. and I'll try to post pics VERY soon! Well, I'm off like a prom dress.. hope to hear from you all VERY soon.. lol

wow, its been like super duper uber long since I've been on here... CUH-razyness.. to the max.. like a hippie!! but yeah, so much has happened, like you have no idea! lets see... I got accepted to college... go me!! ITT tech!! YES!!! um... over christmas break I broke my wrist... I built a snowman and it attacked me... lol.. not really, I was snowboarding... man I'm cool!! lol.. umm... what else? I have finals today and tomorrow.. easy peasy.. is peasy even a word? I don't know.. oh well.. I'm totally watching I love the 90's.. so the greatest show, EVER!! lol.. but yeah... I have a cold, sad day... oh well... huh.. I totally had a brain fart and can't remember anything else now.. lol.. so I'm off.. and all of you better comment... if you know whats good for you.. lol... *shake fist*

so yeah.. I think its finally time for an update.... haha, I start school tomorrow... poop... and lets see, I have Consumer Econ, Food Science (?), Art, Photography, Visual Basic, and Mythology... whoo-hoo... but yeah... its shall be cool... man, I can't beleive its my last year... ack... scary.. but then I'm mad cuz I probably won't be going to UAT in Pheonix, but I'm probably going to ITT tech in Indiana... bah.. but yeah... hmm... I don't know what else to write... my street has become the poster street for birth control... I swear, there are like 22 families on our street and 49 kids... ack.. it sucks... but yeah.. hmm.. this summer was fun, I hung out with my friends and it was all good, but now its school time *sniff* but yeah... I went to the state fair, that was SO much fun... I'd never been to one before here, its awesome... I went twice this year actually, once on a saturday to watch claire and amanda dance, and then on a tuesday with my youth group.. it was SO much fun with the youth group, I hung with claire and my new friend Josh, and he's awesome, for an 8th grader.. hehe... yes... and I made another new friend, Jonathan.. he's cool.. but last year on the bus he annoyed the crap out of me.. hehe... but yes... hmm.. I don't know what else... umm... I'm going to actually LEAVE alaska for christmas... its going to be the first time I've been out of this stupid state since I moved up here.. whoo-hoo... its so icilating up here.. but yeah.. it snowed in the mountians last friday.. its was cool... that was the day I went to claire's swim meet.. yes... very fun.. yay... I got a new cd today.. shinedown.. they're SOoo awesome possum (wow... I've been saying that A LOT lately.. hehe)... but yeah... I have to go now... I must be getting ready for school in the morning.. poop...

So yesterday was cool... I got my Invader Zim DVD and was watching that... and I got to see Steph... and at work my friend Braxton helped me out... and then I saw Chop Stix and Richard and they liked my glasses, and Chop Stix said they were fabulous... which made me kinda scared... and then I found out this guy, Alex, plays hack and we were talking about that, and then he gave me candy... and then when I was cleaning up at work the kitchen flooded.. it was pretty funny.. hehe.. and then I was off early and me and Joe played two games of pool in which he won... and then I came home and watched Zim some more and then I got on the comp and chatted with this awesome guy... (who I'm chatting with this very second)... it was a fun day....
